{"tid":680314,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"波台會員淋紅油 被天眼拍下","createTime":"2018-05-27T06:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T06:32:35.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f93a9cc930208a7acd4878fb366c28f50ef2e975","tid":680314,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:03:04.000Z","msg":"2018年05月27日 <br />\n<br />\n【天眼影晒】淋私家車紅油<br />\n口罩男完事不忘影相<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名戴口罩男子昨凌晨到元朗英龍圍向一輛私家車淋潑紅油，完事後還拍照才離去。整個過程被天眼目擊，女車主報警，警方將案件列作刑事毀壞，正追緝涉案人下落，調查作案動機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現場位於元朗英龍圍一個有蓋停車場，涉事私家車泊於其中一個私人車位中。昨凌晨時分，一名穿黑色上衣牛仔褲、白色波鞋及戴上黑色口罩的男子，手持一個膠袋到場，之後覷準目標私家車，從袋中拿出一樽液體，向車身撥淋紅油，再用手機拍下私家車被淋油的相片後離去，估計是要向上頭交差。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至早上8時許，40歲姓何女車主發現私家車遭人刑毀，立即報警，警方到後向車主了解，事主聲稱從未有與人結怨，警員經翻看附近單位的天眼片段，案件列為刑事毀壞，交由元朗刑事調查隊跟進，正追緝一名約1.5米高的男子。"},{"pid":"0094f6384e88bfd12fa39d4bc1f14cc3eb16e97d","tid":680314,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:03:53.000Z","msg":"他首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3547c78e26df855dda77dd7486c3ac8ab5c30808","tid":680314,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0094f6384e88bfd12fa39d4bc1f14cc3eb16e97d","tid":680314,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:03:53.000Z","msg":"他首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f4aa9e7d06c0e9a69a890a7017bd0efead48ef","tid":680314,"uid":87563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3547c78e26df855dda77dd7486c3ac8ab5c30808","tid":680314,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0094f6384e88bfd12fa39d4bc1f14cc3eb16e97d","tid":680314,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:03:53.000Z","msg":"他首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f64f8fb14ebb5de81832f33d2f5bbc90da7fd2b","tid":680314,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}